{"tid":2119494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁家傑指建制倡延期因憂內地港人拒返港 湯家驊：境外投票的做法可以研究","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T08:46:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b2d32c0be0232a02af3da9ced702d3e4cfec00","tid":2119494,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/WCHYDNOXBQGFZ5N7GYAYMOF7JY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FWCHYDNOXBQGFZ5N7GYAYMOF7JY%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtByK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=11992373\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FWCHYDNOXBQGFZ5N7GYAYMOF7JY%2F&h=1f9e1805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/WCHYDNOXBQGFZ5N7GYAYMOF7JY/</a><br />\n<br />\n至少31個國家地區疫情下都有進行選舉或公投，不少地方也設境外或網上投票、延長投票時間，或安排不同年齡的選民分批投票等，湯家驊認為境外投票的做法可以研究，但未知現時距離投票舉行的時間能否足以處理。他又指，香港人或遍佈全球，不能只偏向某一個群組的選民，要研究應如何處理。"},{"pid":"84925ba7ebc40b340ddbcfa5afbcad46a06d742c","tid":2119494,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"認真討論，唔係通常有領事館先有得搞境外投票咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係有城市or 地區做過境外投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637f71d696d53dbd1941674f599ca8fb97416e37","tid":2119494,"uid":116289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"14億票"},{"pid":"2e0da2b535fe0e2652b251b7de770f7dc1e0d8ec","tid":2119494,"uid":237465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"不如去湯 11 屋企投啦 ! 一定好春方便"},{"pid":"0841dc5c3451812d35c636b86b126e18c74593e0","tid":2119494,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:48:09.000Z","msg"